    "media_coverage_bike": {
      "type": "media-coverage",
      "blocks": {
        "mention_1": {
          "type": "mention",
          "settings": {
            "product": "r8-foldable-exercise-bike-magnetic-resistance",
            "text": "<p>The Ativafit Folding Magnetic Exercise Bike is an affordable and efficient bike. It's smooth, quiet, and offers a range of eight adjustable magnetic resistance levels for variability when training. The frame boasts an X-type design, which creates a compact footprint and allows for easy folding and storage. The Ativafit bike has an adjustable seat, intended to maximize comfort. Featuring an easy-to-read digital monitor and a tablet bracket, the Ativafit Folding Magnetic Exercise Bike could be a great value purchase for a beginner.</p>",
            "link": "https://www.garagegymreviews.com/equipment/ativafit-folding-magnetic-exercise-bike",
            "logo": "shopify://shop_images/garage_review_2081e3bb-bd05-4a3f-8931-d19950655a05.webp",
            "logo_asset": "ggr-new-site-logo.png",
            "logo_bg": false
          }
        },
        "mention_2": {
          "type": "mention",
          "settings": {
            "product": "f8-foldable-exercise-bike",
            "text": "<p>The Ativafit R8 offers a powerful punch for a small price tag. We enjoyed the great workout that this small but robust cycle offered, allowing riders to select their preferred riding position and integrate resistance training into their workout. Depending on what riders are looking for, this workout equipment will check the right boxes for many people looking to purchase equipment in this market.</p>",
            "link": "https://indoorcyclinglove.com/ativafit-r8-foldable-exercise-bike",
            "logo_asset": "Indoor-Cycling-Love-FF-3-01.webp",
            "logo_bg": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "mention_1",
        "mention_2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "STEALING THE SPOTLIGHT",
        "bg_color": "#f5f5f5",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
